Product description

Safety First

  • Our led bathroom mirror is not just a reflection of beauty, but a reflection of your safety. With a built-in explosion-proof film, you could have peace of mind knowing that in the unlikely event of accidental breakage, the glass shards won't scatter. Your safety and that of your loved ones are protected.
  • Experience beauty without compromise, and safety without worry. It's more than a mirror; it's your safeguard.

Waterproof Light Strip

  • With an overall waterproof rating of IP54 and an IP64 waterproof rating for the LED light strip, our illuminated bathroom mirror boldly defies splashes, ensuring you could enjoy life without boundaries.
  • Each meter boasts 192 light beads, shining brighter than ordinary LED mirrors. With a lifespan of up to 50,000 hours, it's your enduring companion. Make each day extraordinary, with a mirror that outshines the rest.
